text:
Reviewer version
We first make a version to help the advisory board making the final selection.


Show code
# wide format data for overview on reviewer assignment and additional check
reviews_wide &lt;- reviews |&gt;
  # remove individual ratings, weights, reviewer names and intervention texts
  select(
    -c(reviewer_name, intervention_name, intervention_mech
       # description, stimulus, tested, citation, outcome_previous_tests, effective, effect_size, comment
       ),
    -any_of(c(rating_vars, paste0(rating_vars, "_weight")))
  ) |&gt; 
  group_by(intervention_id) |&gt;
  mutate(reviewer_slot = row_number()) |&gt;   # 1, 2, 3 within each intervention
  ungroup() |&gt;
  #select(intervention_id, reviewer_slot, reviewer_id, score, reviewer_comments) |&gt;
  pivot_wider(
    names_from = reviewer_slot,
    values_from = c(reviewer_id, score, reviewer_comments),
    names_glue = "{.value}_{reviewer_slot}"
  ) |&gt; 
  arrange(desc(overall_score))


We add simple averages across all reviewers for the ratings on each criterion.


Show code
mean_criteria &lt;-  reviews |&gt; 
  group_by(intervention_id, code_name) |&gt; 
  summarise(
    across(
      all_of(rating_vars),
      ~ mean(.x, na.rm = TRUE),
      .names = "{.col}_mean"
    ),
    .groups = "drop"
  )

reviews_wide &lt;- reviews_wide |&gt; 
  left_join(mean_criteria)


Round all numbers to two digits


Show code
reviews_wide &lt;- reviews_wide |&gt; 
  rounded_numbers()
